 and held many positions including being the past president of the manitoba sports federation  and the former chair of winnipeg’s pan am games  in  riley was inducted into the manitoba sports hall of fame and he is a member of the order of canada    contact us name  email  message  thank you for messaging kelvin history we will get back to you in regards to your question or statement as soon as possible copyright   kelvin history all rights reserved » web development by kelvin graduate morgan wowk board of directors client login         français canada    homebecome a client benefits of richardson gmpclient experience best way to work with ustax  estate planningaccount managementasset safetyfiduciary excellenceonline account accessmoney transfers made simpleheritage successful clientscommunity involvementboard of directorsfinding the right advisorquebec immigration investor program find an advisornews richardson gmp newswirenews  announcementstax  estate planning strategiesmarket outlook quarterly contact us locate a branchfind an investment advisorcustomer supportcareersmedia relationstransparent resolution process nbsp board of directors the richardson gmp board of directors brings together industry veterans with extensive experience across a variety of wealth management disciplines our board also includes two investment advisors to ensure that they bring a client perspective and a voice for all other advisors in how we run our business andrew marsh president  chief executive officer richardson gmp limited a true entrepreneur andrew marsh founded richardson gmp canada’s leading independent wealth management firm and was part of the team that built the firm from the ground up beginning his career in the financial industry over  years ago mr marsh started in investment analysis then worked directly with clients as an investment advisor and eventually his career moved to executive leadership with the launch of gmp private client in  he served as managing director national sales of both gmp private client and richardson gmp before being appointed as president and chief executive officer of richardson gmp in  richardson gmp has since grown a unique partnership culture and leading platform devoted to serving affluent canadian families mr marsh raised the bar for excellence in wealth management by launching richardson gmp insurance our revered tax and estate planning team connected wealth’s asset management team and most recently richardson gmp private family office in our community mr marsh is a member of the board of governors of his alma mater university of guelph and is an active mentor and contributor to the university’s school of business he is also a member of the canadian advisory board for right to play canada a charity dedicated to helping children worldwide through the power of play additionally mr marsh is active in the advocacy efforts in the investment industry association of canada and is a member of the centre for fiduciary excellence   kevin sullivan ba llb cfa deputy chairman gmp capital inc kevin sullivan has been at gmp capital inc since its inception serving as president from  and as ceo of gmp capital from june  to september  he also cofounded gmp securities lp mr sullivan brings over  years of experience and relationships in the capital market industry as ceo of gmp he oversaw the creation and growth of gmp securities lp gmp securities europe llp and gmp investment management lp he also helped facilitate gmp’s ipo in  prior to gmp he spent three years in the european capital market and was also a lawyer in general practice in calgary alberta actively involved with a number of charities and community organizations mrsullivan has cochaired the ride to conquer cancer canada’s premier cycling fundraiser he’s a past member of the princess margaret hospital foundation and a member of the canadian advisory board of right to play h sanford riley president  chief executive officer richardson financial group limited h 